26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_subdev_devinit_base.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:33 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "priv.h"
30
31#include <core/option.h>
32#include <subdev/vga.h>
33
34u32
35nvkm_devinit_mmio(struct nvkm_devinit *init, u32 addr)
36{
37 if (init->func->mmio)
38 addr = init->func->mmio(init, addr);
39 return addr;
40}
41
42int
43nvkm_devinit_pll_set(struct nvkm_devinit *init, u32 type, u32 khz)
44{
45 return init->func->pll_set(init, type, khz);
46}
47
48void
49nvkm_devinit_meminit(struct nvkm_devinit *init)
50{
51 if (init->func->meminit)
52 init->func->meminit(init);
53}
54
55u64
56nvkm_devinit_disable(struct nvkm_devinit *init)
57{
58 if (init && init->func->disable)
59 return init->func->disable(init);
60 return 0;
61}
62
63int
64nvkm_devinit_post(struct nvkm_devinit *init, u64 *disable)
65{
66 int ret = 0;
67 if (init && init->func->post)
68 ret = init->func->post(init, init->post);
69 *disable = nvkm_devinit_disable(init);
70 return ret;
71}
72
73static int
74nvkm_devinit_fini(struct nvkm_subdev *subdev, bool suspend)
75{
76 struct nvkm_devinit *init = nvkm_devinit(subdev);
77 /* force full reinit on resume */
78 if (suspend)
79 init->post = true;
80 return 0;
81}
82
83static int
84nvkm_devinit_preinit(struct nvkm_subdev *subdev)
85{
86 struct nvkm_devinit *init = nvkm_devinit(subdev);
87
88 if (init->func->preinit)
89 init->func->preinit(init);
90
91 /* unlock the extended vga crtc regs */
92 nvkm_lockvgac(subdev->device, false);
93 return 0;
94}
95
96static int
97nvkm_devinit_init(struct nvkm_subdev *subdev)
98{
99 struct nvkm_devinit *init = nvkm_devinit(subdev);
100 if (init->func->init)
101 init->func->init(init);
102 return 0;
103}
104
105static void *
106nvkm_devinit_dtor(struct nvkm_subdev *subdev)
107{
108 struct nvkm_devinit *init = nvkm_devinit(subdev);
109 void *data = init;
110
111 if (init->func->dtor)
112 data = init->func->dtor(init);
113
114 /* lock crtc regs */
115 nvkm_lockvgac(subdev->device, true);
116 return data;
117}
118
119static const struct nvkm_subdev_func
120nvkm_devinit = {
121 .dtor = nvkm_devinit_dtor,
122 .preinit = nvkm_devinit_preinit,
123 .init = nvkm_devinit_init,
124 .fini = nvkm_devinit_fini,
125};
126
127void
128nvkm_devinit_ctor(const struct nvkm_devinit_func *func,
129 struct nvkm_device *device, int index,
130 struct nvkm_devinit *init)
131{
132 nvkm_subdev_ctor(&nvkm_devinit, device, index, 0, &init->subdev);
133 init->func = func;
134 init->post = nvkm_boolopt(device->cfgopt, "NvForcePost", false);
135}
